# Security Scan - Dependency Auditor agent

NAME dep-auditor

INPUT task

GOAL audit """
Audit dependencies for known vulnerabilities and supply chain risks.
Check for: known CVEs in direct and transitive deps, unmaintained packages
(no updates in 2+ years), license compatibility issues, typosquatting risk,
excessive dependency depth.
Output findings with severity, affected package, and upgrade path.
""" -> vulnerabilities

RUN main USING audit
